mall  

  admin 后台管理

    vue-cli3 + webpack + sass || less || stylus + element-ui || iview  + axios 

  server 服务端 

    express + mongodb + jwt  (jsonwebtoken)

  phone   

    vue-cli3 + webpack + sass || less || stylus + vant + axios 

  web || pc   

    vue-cli3 + webpack + sass || less || stylus + 手写样式 + axios 


通用性的骨架    

  1. 测试环境、生产环境、开发环境配置

    .env.development   

      EVN=development   

      VUE_APP_BASE_API = "/api"

    .env.production   
      
      ENV="production"

      VUE_APP_BASE_API = "http://itfly.vip:8888"

    .env.production   
      
      NODE_ENV = production

      ENV = 'staging'

      VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/stage-api'



    "build:prod": "vue-cli-service build",
    "build:stage": "vue-cli-service build --mode staging",
    "dev": "vue-cli-service serve"

  2. axios 的二次封装    

  3. ui   

    vue add element-ui   

  4. vue-router  建议模块化

  5. vuex  状态管理    


